# Urzig, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Urzig (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Kuzhniksky Selsoviet, Tabasaransky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 3 streets.
Geography
Urzig is located 14&nbsp;km west of Khuchni (the district's administrative centre) by road. Kyurek is the nearest rural locality.
